title: Denise Austin & Katie Austin On Personal Fitness, Values, Success, & How To Stay Consistent With Routines
itunes:title: Denise Austin & Katie Austin On Personal Fitness, Values, Success, & How To Stay Consistent With Routines
description:
#464: On today's episode we are joined by the mother daughter duo; Denise & Katie Austin. Denise Austin is an American fitness instructor, author, and columnist, and a former member of the President's Council on Physical Fitness and Sports. Katie is a certified fitness trainer, health coach, author, blogger, model and has been featured on numerous television shows . Today the duo join the show to discuss personal fitness, routines, and success.
